        <div class="content-card">
            <h1>Welcome to Your Dashboard</h1>
            <p>This is your main content area. The sidebar on the left adapts to day and night themes automatically based on the time of day. During the day, you'll see warm golden colors and a bright theme. At night, the sidebar transforms to show cool blues and a dark theme with twinkling stars.</p>
            <p>Press 'T' to manually toggle between day and night themes for testing purposes.</p>
